    <p>
      Sensor data is stored locally in a SQLite database for analysis purposes. No personally identifiable information (PII) is collected.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Data Usage</h2>
    <p>
      Collected data is used for visualization, analysis, and testing. It is not shared with third parties or used for profiling.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Security</h2>
    <p>
      This is a local development project. While basic precautions are taken, this system is not intended for secure or production environments.
    </p>
